But then some nice people came along who gave me a chance. They gave me some time and patience and understanding and love. And now they are my very best special friends that I couldn’t live without!
Maybe somebody out there wants to be my new special friend? Maybe somebody has an empty spot in their home and heart to fill. I just might be your girl!

Koba aka Koba Woba Doo aka Big Papa is officially #HOME and looking dapper on my Coogi comforter ❤️🐾 This boy stole my heart on Christmas at @mtvernonanimals where I volunteer. He was emaciated when they got him in October. It was obvious upon meeting this giant mush that he never belonged in the pound. The sad reality is; none of them do. Even if a dog is “bad”... that’s our fucking fault lol.

I’m filled with so much happiness right now watching him sleep peacefully in my bed.. but he is just one of MILLIONS who need saving. Without us, they will NEVER find that. So yes I just turned Koba’s #HappyTail into a lesson. Rescuing him is the probably the most rewarding thing I’ve ever done. Everyone deserves to know what it’s like to see them realize that their wait is over and they can finally.... just... be a dog.
So if you want a best friend don’t go to your local pet shop and give your money to abusive/overcrowded puppy mills, to a breeder to spend BANK on a dog that has genetic predispositions for diseases (I loved my bell, but it’s true). INSTEAD go to your local shelter or any ACC in NY and rescue a dog. The reality is, most dogs don’t make it out of there whether it be due to lack of funds for training and comfortable living or lack of space. Kennel environments are stressful so even a great dog is likely to succumb to their environment like any human being. Don’t believe the hype around pitbulls or shelter dogs. Know that they are a living being, not an object, but a member of your family. You are most likely their only shot at a second chance. Trust me, they will be grateful.
P.S. : I am still doing music... this right here has always been important to me and a part of my mission to make it. I just decided that I wasn’t gonna wait til I’m rich and famous AF to start making a difference. The time is now so don’t be an ignorant fuck. 😊❤️😂 #AdoptDontShop #MyViciousPitbull #SaveThemAll #NewBestFriend #AdoptLove #KobasStory #WeSpeakForThem
